snippet.title: [ Undertale: No More Deals ] - Trailer #2
snippet.description:
Yeah, I completely remade trailer for NMD
I had to do it because NMD somehow got in UnderEvent, but I'm so proud of result, and it looks way better to me than first version
First version is still public: https://youtu.be/gEkDthnGYfg
You can also check UnderEvent here: https://youtu.be/aOadit6diGE

Track used in trailer was made by MetSon

All other credits and track itself are on GameJolt page that you can check out there: https://gamejolt.com/games/ut-nmd/398695

You can also check out my discord server there: https://discord.gg/bgNAgFYVnS
